{"type":"answer","id":156595,"parentType":"question","parentId":1383,"uid":419,"contents":"补充一下，windows下还有不少好用的开源软件。<br>\n<br>\n多媒体<br>\n音乐播放器: <a href=\"https://www.foobar2000.org\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">foobar2000</a><br>\n全能播放器: <a href=\"https://www.videolan.org\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">VLC</a>、<a href=\"https://mpc-hc.org\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">MPC-HC</a>、<a href=\"https://kodi.tv\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">kodi</a><br>\n转码工具: <a href=\"https://ffmpeg.zeranoe.com/builds/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">ffmpeg</a>（命令行工具，但这个是业内最强最专业的，必须推）<br>\n<br>\n网络<br>\n下载工具: <a href=\"https://ugetdm.com/downloads/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">uGet</a>(内置了aria2，界面与功能兼得), <a href=\"https://transmissionbt.com\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Transmission</a><br>\n匿名上网: <a href=\"https://www.torproject.org\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Tor Browser</a><br>\n公司或熟人内部通讯: <a href=\"https://delta.chat\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">DeltaChat</a><br>\n代理服务器: <a href=\"https://www.privoxy.org\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">privoxy</a>（超难配置，但过滤广告功能强悍无比，也可实现智能分流、socks5代理转http代理等）<br>\nFTP工具: <a href=\"https://filezilla-project.org\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">filezilla</a>（客户端）, <a href=\"https://filezilla-project.org\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">filezilla-server</a>（服务器）<br>\n网络嗅探: <a href=\"https://www.wireshark.org\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">wireshark</a><br>\n<br>\n办公<br>\n绘画工具: <a href=\"https://krita.org\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">krita</a><br>\n3D影片创作: <a href=\"https://www.blender.org\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">blender</a><br>\n文本编辑器: <a href=\"https://www.geany.org\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">geany</a>, <a href=\"http://akelpad.sourceforge.net\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">AkelPad</a><br>\n剪贴板增强: <a href=\"https://ditto-cp.sourceforge.io\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Ditto</a><br>\n<br>\n软件开发<br>\n集成开发工具: <a href=\"https://code.visualstudio.com\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">vscode</a>, <a href=\"https://atom.io\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Atom Editor</a>, <a href=\"https://developer.android.google.cn/studio/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Android Studio</a>, <a href=\"https://spring.io/tools\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Spring Tool Suite</a>, <a href=\"https://www.eclipse.org\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Eclipse</a>, <a href=\"http://www.codeblocks.org\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">CodeBlocks</a><br>\n编译器：<a href=\"http://tdm-gcc.tdragon.net\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">TDM-GCC</a>, <a href=\"http://mingw.org\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">MinGW</a><br>\n文件夹内容比较: <a href=\"http://meldmerge.org\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">meld</a><br>\n离线文档: <a href=\"https://zealdocs.org\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">zeal</a><br>\n<br>\n软件包管理<br>\n<a href=\"https://chocolatey.org\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Chocolatey</a>（命令行，可以安装和更新一堆开源工具）<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.cygwin.com\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">cygwin</a>（移植的一个Linux环境）<br>\n<br>\n终端工具<br>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/microsoft/terminal\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Windows Terminal(Preview)</a><br>\n<br>\n数据安全<br>\n加密磁盘: <a href=\"https://www.veracrypt.fr\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">VeraCrypt</a>（可设真假两个密码，假密码用于对付拷打，呈现虚假的磁盘内容）<br>\n<br>\n其他<br>\n界面美化: <a href=\"http://www.mactype.net\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">MacType</a>（大幅度改善字体渲染）<br>\n<br>\n暂时这么多吧，我算是个伪专家，平时也不怎么用windows","date":"2020-02-08","agreeCount":0,"discussionCount":0}